@* "Paused": In Progress with nobody clocked on (LeafActivity.IsPaused). Carries the same pause sign
   as the Pause job button, and its own neutral-ground colour -- not the amber "someone is working
   now", not the slate "Closed", and emphatically not a warning: this is a valid, ordinary state. *@
<span class="status-pill status-pill-paused">
	<svg class="status-pill-glyph" viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
		<use href="#jt-icon-finish"></use>
	</svg>
	Paused
</span>
